<strong>Gavel of Justice</strong>
<font size=-1>(<a href="/prices/item/gavel_of_justice.shtml">View Going Price</a>)</font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/1h_blunt.shtml">1H Blunt</a><BR>
Damage per second - 3.24<BR>
Damage 5 - Delay 34<BR>
Weight: 7.5 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/shaman/weapons/1h_blunt.shtml">SHM</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (Lore) <BR>
(Mana +5) </font>
<BR>
Obtained through the <a href="/quests/gavel_of_justice.shtml?questID=80">Gavel of Justice</a> quest<BR>

